WEBVTT

00:00:29.664 --> 00:00:31.883
To sam ja za volanom,

00:00:31.883 --> 00:00:35.702
sa svojom sestrom i tadašnjim najboljim prijateljem.

00:00:35.702 --> 00:00:37.825
Jednog dana,

00:00:37.825 --> 00:00:40.932
otac je došao kući, kad sam imao 10-ak godina,

00:00:40.932 --> 00:00:43.236
i za večerom objavio

00:00:43.236 --> 00:00:49.674
da ćemo za sljedeći projekt izgraditi robota.

00:00:49.674 --> 00:00:50.783
Robota.

00:00:50.783 --> 00:00:53.035
Naravno da sam bio ushićen zbog toga

00:00:53.035 --> 00:00:54.625
jer je u školi bio

00:00:54.625 --> 00:00:56.700
nasilnik imenom Kevin,

00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:58.946
koji me maltretirao

00:00:58.946 --> 00:01:01.360
jer sam bio jedini Židov u razredu.